(126, 15, 0, 95, '936acfdd-87e3-5cb8-a86b-ea90dae6013b', 'New research aims to shed light on the social habits of the popular, but often misunderstood, animal.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/02/01/science/groundhogs-animal-behavior.html', 'FALMOUTH, Maine — Groundhog Day may be a tongue-in-cheek holiday, but it remains the one day earmarked in the United States for an animal: Marmota monax, the largest and most widely distributed of the marmot genus, found munching on flowering plants — or, at this time of year, snuggling underground — from Alabama to Alaska.', 'The New York Times', 'merlin_200834691_fc936442-b9cf-4d72-a138-111004384673-articleLarge.jpg', '1643702419', '1683923356'),
(127, 8, 6, 96, '5da54961-32b6-5b88-bad1-2ef7a5f8d670', 'Washington cited “an increase in unusual and concerning Russian military activity near the border with Ukraine.”', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/02/01/world/europe/us-embassy-staff-belarus.html', 'With large-scale Russian military exercises set to begin in Belarus, the United States has ordered the departure of family members of U.S. government employees, citing “an increase in unusual and concerning Russian military activity near the border with Ukraine.”', 'The New York Times', NULL, '1643708778', '1683923357'),
