(130, 20, 0, 99, '07f44eb9-9b6f-59d8-97d6-d4f10e01d772', 'Food is an important part of Lunar New Year celebrations. Do you celebrate? If not, tell us about another holiday that is special to your family.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/02/01/learning/how-do-you-celebrate-your-culture-through-food.html', 'Feb. 1 marks one of the most important holidays in Vietnam, South Korea, China and other Asian countries: Lunar New Year. Do you celebrate this holiday? Are you looking forward to the Year of the Tiger?', 'The New York Times', '29xp-lunarfruits-02-articleLarge.jpg', '1643709604', '1683923362'),
