(232, 20, 0, 0, '108940d6-b4ed-5f77-b99d-7f256b2f542c', 'In recent days, landmarks around the world have been lit in blue and yellow. Why? And what do you think of these displays?', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/03/01/learning/lit-up-landmarks.html', 'Landmarks in New York City like the World Trade Center and the Empire State Building were lit up in recent days in blue and yellow lights. So were other famous landmarks around the world, including the Eiffel Tower, the London Eye, the Colosseum in Rome and the Brandenburg Gate in Berlin.', 'The New York Times', 'merlin_202855098_69140c2a-7bad-4766-b1a6-b5fb193a061a-articleLarge.jpg', '1646121603', '1683923471'),
