(382, 2, 11, 233, '808182ef-77a9-5a18-858d-c156f45e73a4', 'Leisure and hospitality jobs are still far below their pre-Covid levels, but represent a big share of employment gains.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/04/01/business/economy/industries-hit-hard-by-the-pandemic-continued-their-rebound.html', 'The jobs report released Friday — which showed U.S. employers added 431,000 jobs in March on a seasonally adjusted basis — received a round of applause from many economists and labor market analysts, cooling off fears of a major slowdown in growth. And it spurred hope in the service sector that good times may be back again, and stick around more sustainably.', 'The New York Times', NULL, '1648824495', '1683923626'),
