(472, 1, 16, 275, 'd41de688-b5cd-5bae-9944-4e5e8bad3c72', 'Can the Lightning win a third straight championship? Will the Maple Leafs finally win a round? How far can the Rangers go? Will the Panthers’ success in the regular season continue?', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/05/02/sports/hockey/nhl-stanley-cup-playoffs.html', 'The Tampa Bay Lightning are seeking to become the first team to win three straight Stanley Cups since the early ’80s Islanders. But 15 other teams and four rounds of playoffs stand in their way.', 'The New York Times', '02nhl-tampa1-articleLarge.jpg', '1651464068', '1683927134'),
(473, 3, 0, 323, '7c1e5487-7457-50e0-9d29-b6e209c67f29', 'A documentary about college admissions airs on PBS, and Sheryl Crow tells her story in a new Showtime documentary.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/05/02/arts/tv-try-harder-sheryl-crow.html', 'Between network, cable and streaming, the modern television landscape is a vast one. Here are some of the shows, specials and movies coming to TV this week, May 2-8. Details and times are subject to change.', 'The New York Times', '02tvcol-tryharder-articleLarge.jpg', '1651467606', '1683927135'),
(474, 13, 0, 324, 'fd2612e8-3618-5fb4-883e-7743124ee284', 'In a world of war and calamity, the European Union needs to pull together even more.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/05/02/opinion/european-union-macron-ukraine.html', 'BRUSSELS — In July 2020, along with European officials and experts, I was asked to take part in a policy game. Convened by a German think tank, we were asked to play out what would happen if either Matteo Salvini or Marine Le Pen, the far-right leaders in Italy and France, came to power. We spent a few hours frenziedly debating how the European Union would respond to each occurrence. Of one thing we were sure: It would be a disaster.', 'The New York Times', '02degruyer-image-articleLarge.jpg', '1651467606', '1683927136'),
(475, 6, 0, 0, '20232b9b-cfb9-594b-a724-6e52eb9310f3', 'Quotation of the Day for Monday, May 2, 2022.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/05/02/todayspaper/quotation-of-the-day-pandemic-home-market-creates-vast-riches-and-more-inequality.html', '“It’s not that they’re not doing anything; it’s that they’ve aggressively blocked development in so many places.”', 'The New York Times', NULL, '1651467706', '1683927137'),
