(710, 19, 0, 69, '2228c5df-e517-57e4-a521-693ec1f1ca7b', 'President Volodymyr Zelensky urges mass evacuations.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/08/01/briefing/zelensky-donbas-ukraine-evacuation-prison.html', 'Volodymyr Zelensky, the Ukrainian president, urged civilians in the eastern Donbas region to evacuate. The more people leave the Donetsk region now, he said, “the fewer people the Russian Army will have time to kill.”', 'The New York Times', NULL, '1659327888', '1683927408'),
