(713, 3, 3, 453, '36f8c1de-e8e7-55e4-b92d-e49ac84f7653', 'ABC airs footage from the 2022 CMA Fest. And a period drama on Starz wraps up its first season.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/08/01/arts/television/whats-on-tv-cma-fest-becoming-elizabeth.html', 'With network, cable and streaming, the modern television landscape is a vast one. Here are some of the shows, specials and movies coming to TV this week, Aug. 1-7. Details and times are subject to change.', 'The New York Times', '01tvcol-cmafest-articleLarge.jpg', '1659330006', '1683927411'),
