(715, 5, 0, 92, '14c086d1-84ef-5406-bed3-35f57102d02d', 'The Special Victims Division is under federal investigation. Women who were attacked said officers often didn’t know how to investigate, or didn’t bother.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/08/01/nyregion/how-the-nypd-failed-victims-of-sexual-attacks.html', 'Good morning. It’s Monday. More than 2,000 speed cams go into round-the-clock operation today. But first, we’ll take a closer look at the Police Department’s troubled Special Victims Division — and why rape survivors asked the Justice Department to investigate.', 'The New York Times', NULL, '1659331964', '1683927413'),
(716, 4, 0, 0, '639711ef-5c96-5a66-80c1-b297a1b45f66', 'Feeling stuck on today’s puzzle? We can help.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/08/01/crosswords/spelling-bee-forum.html', 'MONDAY — Hi busy bees! Welcome to today’s Spelling Bee forum. There are a number of terms that appear in both this article and other online discussions of the Spelling Bee; a glossary of those terms compiled by Monicat, a Times reader, can be found below. For more Spelling Bee conversation, check out Deb Amlen’s weekly humor column, “Diary of a Spelling Bee Fanatic.”', 'The New York Times', '01bee-forum-mon-articleLarge.jpg', '1659337203', '1683927415'),
(717, 10, 5, 455, 'ad4f5acd-a914-5d76-aafc-61ef437b5382', 'Mark Finchem, a full-throated MAGA warrior, is a leading contender to be Arizona’s next secretary of state. He has said he won’t concede if he loses.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/08/01/us/politics/mark-finchem-arizona-elections.html', 'PHOENIX — This spring, Mark Finchem traveled to Mar-a-Lago for the premiere of a documentary advancing the specious notion that the 2020 presidential election had been stolen from President Donald J. Trump by an army of leftists stuffing drop boxes with absentee ballots. As a state representative and candidate for secretary of state in Arizona, Mr. Finchem was a minnow among the assembled MAGA stars, the likes of Rudolph W. Giuliani and Representative Marjorie Taylor Greene of Georgia.', 'The New York Times', 'merlin_208729557_b4a9cfd0-4378-4c73-a0ec-ea84c424dbb7-articleLarge.jpg', '1659337213', '1683927416'),
(718, 21, 0, 339, '06e4258b-0002-5e36-be45-3a3f40390fc9', 'They were once Democrats and Republicans. But fears for their children in the pandemic transformed their thinking, turning them into single-issue voters for November’s midterms.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/08/01/technology/anti-vax-parents-political-party.html', 'To hear more audio stories from publications like The New York Times, download Audm for iPhone or Android.', 'The New York Times', '00antivax-parents-articleLarge.jpg', '1659337216', '1683927417'),
(719, 8, 6, 456, 'b8c32e9e-b36c-5806-8405-fa9dd6b88bc8', 'A ship loaded with Ukrainian grain left the Port of Odesa for the first time since Russia’s invasion, following an international deal aimed at lowering global food prices.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/video/world/europe/100000008468652/grain-ship-ukraines-odesa.html', 'A ship loaded with Ukrainian grain left the Port of Odesa for the first time since Russia’s invasion, following an international deal aimed at lowering global food prices.', 'The New York Times', NULL, '1659339940', '1683927419'),
