(974, 4, 0, 0, '05068b6f-766f-5d6a-9d01-e968b315bd9e', 'Feeling stuck on today’s puzzle? We can help.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/10/02/crosswords/spelling-bee-forum.html', 'SUNDAY — Hi busy bees! Welcome to today’s Spelling Bee forum. There are a number of terms that appear in both this article and other online discussions of the Spelling Bee; a glossary of those terms compiled by Monicat, a Times reader, can be found below. For more Spelling Bee conversation, check out Deb Amlen’s weekly humor column, “Diary of a Spelling Bee Fanatic.”', 'The New York Times', '02bee-forum-sun-articleLarge.jpg', '1664694003', '1683927673'),
