(1105, 2, 24, 441, 'bf2cf89d-bb9a-5efc-9fc1-1a4652015bf5', 'The onetime crypto mogul also says he’s running out of funds, holed up in the Bahamas.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/11/30/business/dealbook/sam-bankman-fried-parents-net-worth.html', 'The FTX founder Sam Bankman-Fried said on Wednesday that his parents “bore no responsibility” for the downfall of his crypto exchange and the trading arm, Alameda Research, which he founded.', 'The New York Times', '30dealbook-briefing-sbf-broke-swap-1-a5c1-articleLarge.jpg', '1669854175', '1683927804'),
