(1171, 27, 20, 127, '206a4e4f-922c-5a05-8d8a-e4ce23cfb89b', 'The leader of the Oath Keepers was convicted of sedition. How did prosecutors make their case and what does the decision reveal?', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/12/01/podcasts/the-daily/oath-keepers-stewart-rhodes-jan-6-sedition.html', 'In a landmark verdict, a jury convicted Stewart Rhodes, leader of the Oath Keepers, a right-wing militia, of sedition for his role in the Jan. 6 assault on the U.S. Capitol.', 'The New York Times', NULL, '1669892414', '1683927869'),
(1172, 19, 0, 48, 'b1ba8922-1abf-52cd-879f-63a416cda767', 'The rising cost of living can look very different depending on where you live.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/12/01/briefing/interest-rates-mortgage.html', 'Economic policymakers around the world are raising interest rates to try to tame the rising cost of living. Jerome Powell, the Federal Reserve chair, reiterated his commitment to that policy in a speech yesterday. He warned against giving up on inflation “prematurely” and promised to “stay the course until the job is done.”', 'The New York Times', '01-THE-MORNING-NL-housing-articleLarge.jpg', '1669895113', '1683927870'),
(1173, 26, 0, 534, '162a45f1-9c1e-584a-bb90-217b0fb1bc33', 'This documentary highlights Robert Downey Sr.’s charisma and curiosity even when it shows him in decline.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/12/01/movies/sr-robert-downey-review.html', 'In the films he directed in the late 1960s, Robert Downey Sr. credited himself as “A Prince.” It was a private joke typical of the antic artist. As he told Johnny Carson (he was one of a very few “underground filmmakers” to get booked on “The Tonight Show”), “I’m too young to be a king.”', 'The New York Times', 'merlin_217223088_6fb93f2d-e37f-4a56-91ba-79c0063efdfb-articleLarge.jpg', '1669896006', '1683927871'),
(1174, 26, 0, 655, 'b5152610-8cc2-5778-aaa6-64f03257e11e', 'A dense espionage narrative proves all too tangled in this directorial debut from the South Korean actor Lee Jung-jae.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/12/01/movies/hunt-review.html', '“Hunt,” the feature directorial debut of the South Korean actor Lee Jung-jae (a star of “Squid Game”), is a tangled espionage thriller that recalls the suspenseful works of the British novelist John le Carré.', 'The New York Times', '01hunt-review-1-d185-articleLarge.jpg', '1669896006', '1683927872'),
(1175, 9, 0, 656, '121b7f9b-f91b-5bda-b558-793782d4d73c', 'Since the start of the pandemic, the average U.S. renter is working six hours more each month to cover housing costs.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/12/01/realestate/rising-rent-us-cities.html', 'With skyrocketing rents, landlords aren’t just taking more of your cash — they’re spending more of your time.', 'The New York Times', '01calculator-1-3272-articleLarge.jpg', '1669899606', '1683927873'),
(1176, 26, 0, 657, '474104e5-1b97-5acc-bc16-0bbc77ad34d5', 'This film about a small-town pastor hoping to mentor his wife’s killer includes one of the final performances from Anne Heche.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/12/01/movies/what-remains-review.html', 'It’s hard to not watch Anne Heche, who died earlier this year at 53, with a sense of wistfulness in “What Remains,” knowing the role is one of her final ones. The feeling is particularly enhanced by the sense that the actress is both the lone bright spot and somehow the most underutilized presence in a film that struggles to know what it wants to be.', 'The New York Times', 'whatremains1-articleLarge.jpg', '1669900412', '1683927874'),
(1177, 2, 0, 250, '213f0744-4e4d-553c-88c9-413d1b92f994', 'A measure of inflation that the Federal Reserve watches most closely is showing signs of moderation, though price gains still remain too fast for comfort.', 'https://www.nytimes.com/2022/12/01/business/inflation-federal-reserve.html', 'Inflation showed welcome signs of slowing in October, but it remained uncomfortably rapid even as a spate of economic data underscored that a return to normal price increases could take time.', 'The New York Times', '01dc-inflation-1-eb8d-articleLarge.jpg', '1669901780', '1683927875'),
